00261 static inline
00262 CSL_CdcRequestRet CDC_reqClearFeature(CSL_UsbDevHandle      devHandle,
00263                                       CSL_UsbSetupStruct    *usbSetup,
00264                                       CSL_UsbEpHandle       hInEp,
00265                                       CSL_UsbEpHandle       hOutEp,
00266                                       void                  *pCdc)
00267 {
00268     CSL_CdcRequestRet    retStat;
00269     CSL_UsbEpHandle      hEPx;
00270     Uint16               endpt;  /* this is USB logical endpoint */
00271 
00272     retStat = CSL_CDC_REQUEST_SEND_ACK;
00273 
00274     switch(usbSetup->wValue)
00275     {
00276         case CSL_USB_FEATURE_ENDPOINT_STALL:
00277             endpt = (usbSetup->wIndex) & CSL_CDC_8BIT_MASK;
00278             hEPx = USB_epNumToHandle(devHandle, endpt);
00279             USB_clearEndptStall(hEPx);
00280             break;
00281 
00282         case CSL_USB_FEATURE_REMOTE_WAKEUP:
00283             USB_setRemoteWakeup(devHandle, (CSL_UsbBoolean)FALSE);
00284             break;
00285 
00286         default:
00287             /* Unsupported Feature. STALL the endpoint */
00288             retStat = CSL_CDC_REQUEST_STALL;
00289             break;
00290     }
00291 
00292     return(retStat);
00293 }

00349 static inline
00350 CSL_CdcRequestRet CDC_reqGetStatus(CSL_UsbDevHandle      devHandle,
00351                                    CSL_UsbSetupStruct    *usbSetup,
00352                                    CSL_UsbEpHandle       hInEp,
00353                                    CSL_UsbEpHandle       hOutEp,
00354                                    void                  *pCdc)
00355 {
00356     CSL_CdcRequestRet     retStat;
00357     pCdcClassHandle       pCdcClassHdl;
00358     CSL_CdcCtrlObject     *pCtrlHandle;
00359     CSL_UsbEpHandle       hEPx;
00360     CSL_Status            status;
00361     Uint16                endpt;   /* this is USB logical endpoint */
00362 
00363     pCdcClassHdl = (pCdcClassHandle)(pCdc);
00364     pCtrlHandle  = &pCdcClassHdl->ctrlHandle;
00365     retStat      = CSL_CDC_REQUEST_GET_ACK;
00366 
00367     switch(usbSetup->bmRequestType - CSL_CDC_REQUEST_TYPE_BASE)
00368     {
00369         /* Device Status to be returned */
00370         case CSL_CDC_REQUEST_TYPE_DEVICE_STATUS:
00371             pCtrlHandle->ctrlBuffer[0] =
00372             (((Uint16)USB_getRemoteWakeupStat(devHandle))<<1) |
00373              CSL_CDC_CURRDEV_STAT;
00374             USB_postTransaction(hInEp, 2, &pCtrlHandle->ctrlBuffer,
00375                                 CSL_USB_IOFLAG_NONE);
00376             break;
00377 
00378         /* Interface status is to be returned */
00379         case CSL_CDC_REQUEST_TYPE_INTERFACE_STATUS:
00380             pCtrlHandle->ctrlBuffer[0] = CSL_CDC_CURRDEV_STAT;
00381             USB_postTransaction(hInEp, 2, &pCtrlHandle->ctrlBuffer,
00382                                 CSL_USB_IOFLAG_NONE);
00383             break;
00384 
00385         /* Endpoint status to be returned */
00386         case CSL_CDC_REQUEST_TYPE_EP_STATUS:
00387 
00388             endpt  =  usbSetup->wIndex & 0xFF;
00389             hEPx   =  USB_epNumToHandle(devHandle, endpt);
00390             pCtrlHandle->ctrlBuffer[0] = (Uint16)USB_getEndptStall(hEPx,
00391                                                                    &status);
00392             USB_postTransaction(hInEp, 2, &pCtrlHandle->ctrlBuffer,
00393                                 CSL_USB_IOFLAG_NONE);
00394             break;
00395 
00396         default:
00397             /* STALL the endpoint */
00398             retStat = CSL_CDC_REQUEST_STALL;
00399             break;
00400     }
00401 
00402     return(retStat);
00403 }

00460 CSL_CdcRequestRet CDC_reqSetFeature(CSL_UsbDevHandle      devHandle,
00461                                     CSL_UsbSetupStruct    *usbSetup,

00471

00482             USB_setRemoteWakeup(devHandle, (CSL_UsbBoolean)TRUE);
00483             break;
00484 
00485         default:
00486             /* Feature not supported, STALL the endpoint */
00487             retStat = CSL_CDC_REQUEST_STALL;
00488             break;
00489     }
00490 
00491   return(retStat);

00624 static inline
00625 CSL_CdcRequestRet CDC_reqGetMaxLUN(CSL_UsbDevHandle      devHandle,
00626                                    CSL_UsbSetupStruct    *usbSetup,
00627                                    CSL_UsbEpHandle       hInEp,
00628                                    CSL_UsbEpHandle       hOutEp,
00629                                    void                  *pCdc)
00630 {
00631     pCdcClassHandle       pCdcClassHdl;
00632     CSL_CdcCtrlObject*    pCtrlHandle;
00633     CSL_CdcRequestRet     retStat;
00634 
00635     pCdcClassHdl = (pCdcClassHandle)(pCdc);
00636     pCtrlHandle  = &pCdcClassHdl->ctrlHandle;
00637     pCtrlHandle->ctrlBuffer[1] = pCdcClassHdl->cdcHandle.noOfPort;
00638 
00639     /*
00640      * Verify the setup packet fields
00641      * wValue - 0
00642      * wIndex - interface number, set 0
00643      * wLength - 1
00644      */
00645     if ((usbSetup->wIndex == 0) &&
00646         (usbSetup->wLength == 1) &&
00647         (usbSetup->wValue == 0))
00648     {
00649         USB_postTransaction(hInEp, 1, &pCtrlHandle->ctrlBuffer[0],
00650                             CSL_USB_IOFLAG_NONE);
00651 
00652         /* Receive a 0 length packet for acknowledgement */
00653         retStat = CSL_CDC_REQUEST_GET_ACK;
00654     }
00655     else
00656     {
00657         retStat = CSL_CDC_REQUEST_STALL;
00658     }
00659 
00660     return (retStat);
00661 }

00718 static inline
00719 CSL_CdcRequestRet CDC_reqGetInterface(CSL_UsbDevHandle      devHandle,
00720                                       CSL_UsbSetupStruct    *usbSetup,
00721                                       CSL_UsbEpHandle       hInEp,
00722                                       CSL_UsbEpHandle       hOutEp,
00723                                       void                  *pCdc)
00724 {
00725     pCdcClassHandle       pCdcClassHdl;
00726     CSL_CdcCtrlObject     *pCtrlHandle;
00727     CSL_CdcRequestRet     retStat;
00728 
00729     pCdcClassHdl = (pCdcClassHandle)(pCdc);
00730     pCtrlHandle  = &pCdcClassHdl->ctrlHandle;
00731     retStat      = CSL_CDC_REQUEST_GET_ACK;
00732 
00733     /* Compare the Interface with the bNumInterfaces byte of Configuration Descriptor */
00734     if(usbSetup->wIndex == 0)
00735     {
00736         /* Send the current Interface Value */
00737         pCtrlHandle->ctrlBuffer[1] = 0;
00738         USB_postTransaction(hInEp, 1, &pCtrlHandle->ctrlBuffer[0],
00739                             CSL_USB_IOFLAG_NONE);
00740     }
00741     else
00742     {
00743         /*  Interface specified doesn't exist, STALL the endpoint */
00744         retStat = CSL_CDC_REQUEST_STALL;
00745     }
00746 
00747     return retStat;
00748 }
